title: 窶気ory Wells, Three Dog Night singer, dies at 74
text: 窶気ory Wells, Three Dog Night singer, dies at 74 Thursday, 22 October 2015 (4 minutes ago) Wells was the lead singer on such hits as "Never Been to Spain" and "Mama Told Me (Not to Come)" Camera Obscura Keyboardist Carey Lander Dies 01:14 Camera Obscura keyboardist and singer Carey Lander has died at the age of thirty-three after battling a rare bone cancer for four years. Back in 2011, the musician was diagnosed, but continued to play with the band until August when she took a break from her music career to focus on her health. Since...
